{
  "stem": "27770.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then we find out that, if it's a rainy day, don't go to the wire.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So this Kanada, what I've told you is there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There, they had it was with mostly women that are there, not men only women.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the ladies' room, when-- there was a special kapo, a foreman, to take her on the ladies' room-- forgive me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because if somebody didn't want to work too many hours, he went to the ladies' room just to waste time, not to do the work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But all of them, and as many as they opened up all this clothing, these shoes, in pockets, in buttons, in coats, in hats, every Jew brought, or a coin or a diamond.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Instead of then-- they told them to report if for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All they did, everything went, they gave in some.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they couldn't say nobody has it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But 90% of them, went to the toilet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In this toilet, what was diamonds there, you can buy a few Rockefeller Centers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the later on, they was sending-- they was-- all of us, sending all kind of stuff, food or something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one day, they caught one of the girl, who was throwing a package.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She could be about 18, 19 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Came the German, a sadistic, young SS, maybe he was 20, 22 years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And with a walking stick, she had to get, on behind, 25 lashes on her behind.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Only the three, four lashes, she was screaming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She didn't screen any more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When they took out from the chair, not half-dead, but I would say 90% dead.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because they took her in, and the SS told it like this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Not for her, because she was not conscious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Tomorrow morning, if she's not attending to work, she goes to crematorium.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
